[4mOVERVIEW[0m
Output the chromosome, start position, and stop position in bed format

[4mAVAILABLE FIELDS[0m
  [1mstop[0m
    The end position of the variant. Zero-based, exclusive
  [1mchromosome_name[0m
    Chromosome: an identifier from the reference genome or an angle-bracketed ID String ("<ID>")
    pointing to a contig in the assembly file
  [1mstart[0m
    The start position of the variant. Zero-based

